text: Martine McCutcheon (born Martine Kimberley Sherrie Ponting on 14 May 1976) is a British actress and singer. She was born in Hackney, London. She played Tiffany Mitchell in EastEnders from 1995 to 1998. She played Natalie in Love Actually. In September 2012, McCutcheon married singer Jack McManus. On 4 February 2015, she gave birth to her son, Rafferty Jack McManus.
